<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>397</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hi vawlei hi dawh tein, Van zong khi khuaruahhar in, Nangmah nih na
 ser hna i, Na dawtnak a langh caah.

[C1]
   Zeizong Bawi nangmah sinah, Hi lunglawmhnak hla kan sa.

[V2]
 Chun le zan chung a ummi, A sungmi caantha vialte, Tlang le nel,
 thingkung, pangpar, Ni, thla, arfi ceunak ca'h.

[C2]
   Zeizong Bawi nangmah sinah, Hi lunglawmhnak hla kan sa.

[V3]
 Pakhat le pakhat dawtnak, Unau, nu, pa fale hna, Lei le vancung ummi
 hawi, Nunnem ruahnak vialte ca'h.

[C3]
   Zeizong Bawi nangmah sinah, Hi lunglawmhnak hla kan sa.

[V4]
 Zungzal in nangmah sinah, Thlacammi na Khrihfabu, Dawtnak kha khua
 zakip ah, A kalpitu caah hin.

[C4]
   Zeizong Bawi nangmah sinah, Hi lunglawmhnak hla kan sa.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<title>HI VAWLEI HI DAWH TEIN CH397</title>
</song>